full_summary:
### Borescope Kits

#### Public Notice

**Reference Number:** PW-22-01006856  
**Amendment Number:** 3  
**Solicitation Number:** W8485-227044/A  
**Publication Date:** September 12, 2022  
**Tender Closing Date:** October 12, 2022, 14:00:00 hours  
**Amendment Date:** October 12, 2022  
**Expected Contract Start Date:** None  
**Expected Contract End Date:** None  
**Tender Status:** Expiré

**Goods/Services Description:**

The Department of National Defence is soliciting bids for the procurement of Borescope Kits, to be delivered to 4 Wing Cold Lake and 3 Wing Bagotville. The scope of the acquisition includes:

* Borescope Kits
* Software (if applicable)
* Training
* User and Maintenance Manuals

**Quantity and Unit of Issue:**

* Item 1: 11 ea to be delivered to 4 Wing Cold Lake
* Item 2: 9 ea to be delivered to 3 Wing Bagotville
* Item 3: Calibration requirements to be delivered to 4 Wing Cold Lake
* Item 4: Calibration requirements to be delivered to 3 Wing Bagotville
* Item 5: In-Service Support (as required) to be delivered to 4 Wing Cold Lake
* Item 6: In-Service Support (as required) to be delivered to 3 Wing Bagotville
* Item 7 (optional): Borescope Kits to be delivered to 4 Wing Cold Lake and 3 Wing Bagotville

**Trade Agreements:**

* Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA)
* Canada-Ukraine Free Trade Agreement (CUFTA)
* Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA)
* Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
* Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA)
* Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (CPTPP)
* Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA)
* World Trade Organization Agreement on Government Procurement (WTO GPA)

**Contact Information:**

Marie-andree Fortin  
Department of National Defence  
101 Colonel By Dr, Ottawa, ON K1A0K2  
Phone: 819-939-8856  
Email: [marie-andree.fortin@forces.gc.ca](mailto:marie-andree.fortin@forces.gc.ca
